      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation activities must use geometry, flow conditions, and fluid properties representative of the CPB device operating envelope.",
      "rationale": "Validation performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump, which shares geometric and hydrodynamic similarity with the subject device. Operating conditions span the clinical CPB envelope."
