      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental sample characterization (blood source, hematocrit, storage conditions) documented in FDA dataset; statistical analysis not required at MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "FDA benchmark dataset includes sample characterization metadata. Formal statistical treatment of sample variability not required at MRL 2. Factor accepted as not-assessed per assessment plan."
